---
title: Hidden Veggie, Beef & Lentil Lasagne with Parmesan Cheese
description: Construction is key when making a good lasagne but maybe more importantly is what you pack in. Lay a sheet of lasagne and
begin adding the rich tomato sauce dotted with hidden sautéed veggies and beef. Then another lasagne sheet and more sauce and more
and more! Don’t forget the Parmesan to give this extravaganza an extra zap.
